      {
        "title": "Price to preformance AMD is known for!!!",
        "text": "Nothing but positive feedback here. Went from a 2060 to a 9060xt and amd impressed me quite a bit with the adrenalin software and customization options.\n\nMoved up to the 9070xt for 1440p monitor I got and it hits the price to preformance sweet spot amd is well known for.\n\nAll games handle ultra settings 1440p no issue over 100fps and looks great. This card hits its mark falling shortly behind nvidias 5070 ti counterpart. If your not a ray tracing ai generated frames fan boy this card will handle all your needs and ask for more while doing so.......",
