        "title": "Runs like a dream",
        "text": "My family is thrilled with the performance of our new video card! The jump in performance for Hogwarts Legacy, our pickiest game, was sounding! AMD for life if they keep up good work like this!\n\nWe had an excellent setup for airflow, so we are, at least for now, able to run this on quiet mode (it isn't silent, but it's actually much quieter than our prior video card). 4k feed runs as expected (very well) to our \"monitor\" which is our living room TV (77\" Sony Bravia 2024 model). I'll have to troubleshoot further if we wish to use VRR though, as the common fixes for blinks on mouse movement within Windows 11 did not resolve our issue. For now we are set as \"enhanced\" without VRR. Honestly, it's been so wonderful overall that I'm not sure I'll put further time or trouble into that.",
